{"tid":2128900,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"北京批評新西蘭對香港國安法錯誤解讀　促立即糾正","createTime":"2020-07-28T08:49:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T09:57:54.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e3e58ddeae3ac8019567ee19849467de0114118e","tid":2128900,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T08:49:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1540340-20200728.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1540340-20200728.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=oFI5KSBgBGvHra6dYUznBr32HZRMtn4xjJY4gFhUisg%3D&h=ec17ccd6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1540340-20200728.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=3633a5cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1540340-20200728.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n新西蘭政府宣布暫停執行與香港的引渡協議。<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部發言人汪文斌回應，新西蘭的舉措完全建立在對香港國安法的錯誤解讀之上。新方的做法嚴重違反國際法和國際關係基本準則，粗暴干涉中國內政，中方對此表示強烈反對，並保留作出進一步反應的權利。<br />\n<br />\n他說，中國政府維護國家主權安全發展利益的決心堅定不移，反對外部勢力干預香港事務的決心堅定不移，任何對華施壓的圖謀都絕不會得逞。<br />\n<br />\n中方敦促新方立即糾正錯誤，停止以任何方式干涉香港事務和中國內政，以免給中新關係造成損害。"},{"pid":"7ccc75d6044e31bf4cb68c0beb2da60acb733988","tid":2128900,"uid":83348,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T08:52:17.000Z","msg":"全世界知識分子都解讀錯，係得你中共有解釋權任你解釋"},{"pid":"9d74d01d707959cef97bbbf911b857151b0a8035","tid":2128900,"uid":592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T08:53:16.000Z","msg":"開始眾叛親離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d35eda5bce15cce2467d4dafc9ee1edbd584b30f","tid":2128900,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T09:01:20.000Z","msg":"個個都錯！得我習帝啱！"},{"pid":"8d50b3f253e3329343be6909f9eddcb2a84baae5","tid":2128900,"uid":28913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T09:57:54.000Z","msg":"個個都理解錯, 得你中國識理解<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你鐘意點曲解事實都變左慣例啦<br />\n<br />\n外國信你中國都有撚味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n十足十比人捉姦d 八婆屈人誤解佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}